'''伊利亚·羅曼諾維奇·普里高津[[子爵|子爵]]'''（{{lang-ru|'''Илья́ Рома́нович Приго́жин'''}}，{{lang-en|'''Ilya Romanovich Prigogine'''}}，{{bd|1917年|1月25日|2003年|5月28日|catIdx=Prigogine}}），[[比利时|比利时]][[化学家|化学家]]、[[物理学家|物理学家]]，1977年[[诺贝尔化学奖|诺贝尔化学奖]]获得者，[[非平衡态统计物理|非平衡态统计物理]]与[[耗散结构理论|耗散结构理论]]奠基人。

==生平==
1917年，伊利亚·羅曼諾維奇·普里高津出生於[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的[[猶太人|猶太人]]家庭，幾個月之後[[十月革命|十月革命]]爆發<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=3-G3vi5av28C&pg=PA80&lpg=PA80&dq=prigogine+anti+semitic#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Francis Leroy. A century of Nobel Prizes recipients: chemistry, physics, and medicine (p. 80) |publisher=Books.google.com |accessdate=2012-03-12|isbn=9780203014189 |date=2003-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1431987/Vicomte-Ilya-Prigogine.html |title=Vicomte Ilya Prigogine (Obituary, The Telegraph) |publisher=Telegraph.co.uk |date=2003-06-05 |accessdate=2012-03-12 |archive-date=2014-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102000047/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1431987/Vicomte-Ilya-Prigogine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=_80mmfL-i0MC&pg=PA227&lpg=PA227&dq=prigogine+jewish#v=onepage&q=prigogine%20jewish&f=false |title=Magnus Ramage, Karen Shipp. Systems Thinkers (p. 227) |publisher=Books.google.com |accessdate=2012-03-12|isbn=9781848825253 |date=2009-09-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storyCode=108305&sectioncode=26 |title=Andrew Robinson. Time and notion |publisher=Timeshighereducation.co.uk |date=1998-07-17 |accessdate=2012-03-12 |archive-date=2012-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120083910/http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storyCode=108305&sectioncode=26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chaosforum.com/docs/denkers/column7.html |title=Time and Change |publisher=Chaosforum.com |date=2003-05-28 |accessdate=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425092616/http://www.chaosforum.com/docs/denkers/column7.html |archive-date=2012-04-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://pagerankstudio.com/Blog/2010/09/ilya-prigogine-biography-life-and-career-facts-invented/ |title=Biography of Ilya Prigogine |publisher=Pagerankstudio.com |access